<x-mail::message :subject="'C79 ('.$data['subject'].')'" :lang="''.$data['lang'].''"><p>Dear {{ $data['client']['client_firstname'] }} {{ $data['client']['client_lastname'] }}</p><p>Please find attached your C79 Import VAT certificate: {{ $data['subject'] }}</p><p>Kindly note that you need to keep this document stored together with your other British accounting-related material, for a minimum of 6 years from issue date.</p><p>We must further bring to your attention that your freight forwarder(s)/carrier(s), mentioned in the C79 document, have imported your goods without using your Postponed VAT Account. Therefore, you are kindly requested to contact your freight forwarder(s)/carrier(s) and ask them to use your Postponed VAT Account for future shipments.</p><p>{{ $data['message'] }}</p><p>Best regards</p><p>{{ $data['client']['team_user_firstname'] }}</p><p>{{ $data['client']['team_user_designation'] }}</p><p>{{ $data['app_name'] }}</p></x-mail::message>